        content:
          "Uznews, Tashkent, 08 Sep 2008 – While waiting for his trial, Salijon Abdurahmanov, Uznews.net's correspondent in Karakalpakstan and human rights activist, has written a letter to the Uzbek prosecutor-general in which he detailed charges trumped up against him but it has not been answered yet.",
